# Spanish (Castilian/neutral Latin American) translation for Powerbuilder UI.
# DRAFT — flagged for native-speaker review before any production rollout.
# Translator notes: tone is warm but professional, leaning Latin American
# neutral (no peninsular vosotros). Tú-form address everywhere; usted only
# in formal mailers (which are not in the UI surface). Mirror the casual,
# action-oriented voice of the English source. Do NOT translate proper
# nouns: Powerbuilder, OpenAI, Pinecone, Census API, FEC, Gwinnett, Beta.
#
